==Overview==
Very fast and very fragile, the '''Skull Crusher''', also known as '''Scorpion''' by the Argon military, packs a huge punch for its class and when used correctly is a supreme interceptor.

==Background==
A forerunner of this ship fought in the Boron Campaign and proved to be a pilot favorite. Like most other [[Split]] ships, this design focuses on high-speed engines and increased weapons power, at the cost of shield strength. Over the years the ship has been frequently updated and rearmed in order to remain as deadly as possible.

