==Physical Characteristics==
Like all Split fighters, the Scorpion has a triangular, dagger-shaped hull and short, pointed wings.  It differs from its big brother, the [[Mamba]], primarily in size.

== Combat ==
The Scorpion is the smallest craft to mount both the powerful [[HEPT]] and [[Pulsed Beam Emitter|PBE]], allowing it to demolish another [[M4]] with relative ease. However, its weak shielding and paltry energy weapon generator is a big problem, which must be worked around either by flying it very evasively and carefully, or by using a pack that can demolish their prey before it gets a chance to fire back.

